{"name":"五行篇","type":"中国哲学","description":"五行","example":" 不悦不戚心悦而後能戚心所戚心 不敬不严严犹敬之责积者也 不尊不恭恭也者用上敬下也 不仁不安仁而能安天道也 不爱不仁爱而後仁 ","words":[{"word":"不爱不仁爱而後仁","pinyin":"bu'ai'bu'ren'ai'er'hou'ren"},{"word":"不间简不行行也者言其所行之","pinyin":"bu'jian'jian'bu'xing'xing'ye'zhe'yan'qi'suo'xing'zhi"},{"word":"不敬不严严犹敬之责积者也","pinyin":"bu'jing'bu'yan'yan'you'jing'zhi'ze'ji'zhe'ye"},{"word":"不戚心不亲戚心而後能亲之","pinyin":"bu'qi'xin'bu'qin'qi'xin'er'hou'neng'qin'zhi"},{"word":"不亲不爱亲而後能爱之","pinyin":"bu'qin'bu'ai'qin'er'hou'neng'ai'zhi"},{"word":"不仁不安仁而能安天道也","pinyin":"bu'ren'bu'an'ren'er'neng'an'tian'dao'ye"},{"word":"不行不义义也","pinyin":"bu'xing'bu'yi'yi'ye"},{"word":"不严不尊严而後忌己尊","pinyin":"bu'yan'bu'zun'yan'er'hou'ji'ji'zun"},{"word":"不悦不戚心悦而後能戚心所戚心","pinyin":"bu'yue'bu'qi'xin'yue'er'hou'neng'qi'xin'suo'qi'xin"},{"word":"不尊不恭恭也者用上敬下也","pinyin":"bu'zun'bu'gong'gong'ye'zhe'yong'shang'jing'xia'ye"},{"word":"恭而後礼也有以体礼气也","pinyin":"gong'er'hou'li'ye'you'yi'ti'li'qi'ye"},{"word":"赫赫圣貌也言","pinyin":"he'he'sheng'mao'ye'yan"},{"word":"经目侔而知之谓之进之","pinyin":"jing'mu'mou'er'zhi'zhi'wei'zhi'jin'zhi"},{"word":"仁义心也同则善耳","pinyin":"ren'yi'xin'ye'tong'ze'shan'er"},{"word":"圣人知天之道道者所道也","pinyin":"sheng'ren'zhi'tian'zhi'dao'dao'zhe'suo'dao'ye"},{"word":"士有志於君子道谓之志士","pinyin":"shi'you'zhi'yu'jun'zi'dao'wei'zhi'zhi'shi"},{"word":"诗曰不不救不刚不柔此之谓也","pinyin":"shi'yue'bu'bu'jiu'bu'gang'bu'rou'ci'zhi'wei'ye"},{"word":"是之谓独独也者舍体也","pinyin":"shi'zhi'wei'du'du'ye'zhe'she'ti'ye"},{"word":"说不简不行间简也间简则行矣","pinyin":"shuo'bu'jian'bu'hang'jian'jian'ye'jian'jian'ze'xing'yi"},{"word":"说金声而玉振之","pinyin":"shuo'jin'sheng'er'yu'zhen'zhi"},{"word":"说尸鸟鸠在桑直之也","pinyin":"shuo'shi'niao'jiu'zai'sang'zhi'zhi'ye"},{"word":"四行之所和言和仁义也","pinyin":"si'hang'zhi'suo'he'yan'he'ren'yi'ye"},{"word":"所安所行所敬人道也","pinyin":"suo'an'suo'xing'suo'jing'ren'dao'ye"},{"word":"形则圣圣","pinyin":"xing'ze'sheng'sheng"},{"word":"以其中心与人交悦也壳壳","pinyin":"yi'qi'zhong'xin'yu'ren'jiao'yue'ye'ke'ke"},{"word":"玉音则圣形","pinyin":"yu'yin'ze'sheng'xing"},{"word":"远而庄之敬也敬者","pinyin":"yuan'er'